short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension for downloading the attendance on Google Meet and also you can enable auto admit.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension for downloading the attendance of the attendees on Google Meet and also you can enable auto admit so that people want to join the meeting can be admitted automatically and you don't get disturbed each and every time granting permissions.
